            <h1>EV Charging Stations in Pune</h1>
            <p>Find the best EV charging stations in Pune, from fast chargers on highway routes to convenient city and shared chargers.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container container--narrow">
            <div class="card reveal" style="margin-bottom:40px;">
                <h2>Pune charging hotspots</h2>
                <p>Pune is building a strong EV charging network across Hinjewadi, Magarpatta, Kalyani Nagar, Baner, and the Mumbai-Pune Expressway corridor. These areas now host both public and private charging locations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card reveal" style="margin-bottom:40px;">
                <h2>Fast chargers in Pune</h2>
                <p>For quick top-ups, focus on DC fast chargers and high-power AC chargers. Search for stations near business parks, malls, and highway rest stops to minimize waiting time.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card reveal" style="margin-bottom:40px;">
                <h2>Shared chargers and peer-to-peer options</h2>
                <p>ChargeKr makes it easy to discover shared chargers from homes and businesses in Pune. These chargers can be useful when public networks are busy or when you need a convenient city charging option.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card reveal" style="margin-bottom:40px;">
                <h2>How to choose a Pune charger</h2>
                <div class="feature-list">
                    <div class="feature-list-item"><span class="check"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i></span><div><strong>Check connector compatibility:</strong> Ensure the charger matches your EV’s connector.</div></div>
                    <div class="feature-list-item"><span class="check"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></span><div><strong>Read reviews:</strong> Pick chargers with good feedback for reliability and safety.</div></div>
                    <div class="feature-list-item"><span class="check"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></span><div><strong>Reserve when possible:</strong> Booking ahead reduces uncertainty during peak hours.</div></div>
                </div>
            </div>

